response.overview: From Birmingham, a nationwide Jubilee party with Blue Peter regulars, CBBC stars and UK pop acts including Gareth Gates and S Club Juniors. Liz Barker opens a National Gallery exhibition of the top 50 portraits of the Queen, painted by Blue Peter viewers, Konnie Huq joins choristers at St Paul's Cathedral preparing to sing before Her Majesty, while Matt Baker reveals the answers to the Post the Palace feature. Free Blue Peter magazine
response.title: Blue Peter Jubilee Party
